Technology recognizes sound signals and converts them into dynamic vibrations so that players can feel the game without installing additional software.
By using the sense of touch, the sound signals can accurately imitate the action in the game.
Razer HyperSense plays events – from silent steps to powerful explosions, giving precise all activities around the player.
